stimulus:
Please carefully read the following campaign, and indicate below how much you would donate.

Once you are satisfied, press "Continue" at the bottom.

responses: {"Q0":"Jason was diagnosed with Stage II lymphoma and will need many treatments including chemotherapy which he started last week.  His friend has started a campaign to help raise funds to cover the cost of treatments and hospital bills so any donations are helpful."}
{"Q0":"To see how people react to crowdfunding donations when they know they could either keep the money or donate the money.  And to see how charitable people may be."}
